# JobAgent Alembic migrations

Application-owned SQLite schema only (eleven tables). LangGraph checkpoint
tables are owned later by the checkpointer and must not appear here.

Local upgrade (from `backend/`, with root env or `SQLITE_PATH` set):

```text
python -m alembic -c alembic.ini upgrade head
```

Do not add automatic downgrade/reset scripts. Upgrade is safe to re-run against
an already-initialized persistent SQLite file.
